Ranger Help for: longfire
=========================

SYNTAX:      longfire <direction> at <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     60
SKILL TYPE:  archery

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to fire a longbow shot into an adjacent room,
striking a target from a distance without entering the room. The Ranger
must specify the direction and the target. A longbow must be wielded
with an arrow readied. This is a powerful tactical skill that lets the
Ranger engage enemies before they can close to melee range. Damage is
based on archery skill and dexterity.
